            "content": "{\n  \"files\": [\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/schedule.go\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/alert_rule.go\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/recording_rule.go\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/ticker/ticker.go\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/metrics/scheduler.go\"}\n  ],\n  \"symbols\": [\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/schedule.go\", \"symbol\": \"schedulePeriodic\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/schedule.go\", \"symbol\": \"processTick\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/schedule.go\", \"symbol\": \"runJobFn\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/ticker/ticker.go\", \"symbol\": \"T.run\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/alert_rule.go\", \"symbol\": \"alertRule.Eval\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/recording_rule.go\", \"symbol\": \"recordingRule.Eval\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/metrics/scheduler.go\", \"symbol\": \"Scheduler.EvaluationMissed\"}\n  ],\n  \"chain\": [\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/schedule.go\", \"symbol\": \"schedulePeriodic\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/schedule.go\", \"symbol\": \"processTick\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/schedule.go\", \"symbol\": \"runJobFn\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/alert_rule.go\", \"symbol\": \"alertRule.Eval\"},\n    {\"repo\": \"grafana/grafana\", \"path\": \"pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/ticker/ticker.go\", \"symbol\": \"T.run\"}\n  ],\n  \"text\": \"The Grafana alerting evaluation scheduler is implemented in pkg/services/ngalert/schedule/schedule.go. The main entry point is the Run() method which calls schedulePeriodic() (line 246), the core scheduler loop. This loop receives ticks from ticker.T (ticker/ticker.go:51) which generates regular ticks at the configured baseInterval. For each tick, processTick() (line 276) is called to determine which alert rules are ready for evaluation based on their evaluation intervals.\\n\\nAlert rule evaluations are scheduled by runJobFn() (line 426), which sends evaluations to individual rule routines via their Eval() method. The Eval() method in alert_rule.go (line 200) and recording_rule.go (line 113) handles evaluation sending with built-in overrun detection: before sending a new evaluation, it attempts a non-blocking read from the evaluation channel. If a previous evaluation is still waiting to be processed, that dropped evaluation is returned.\\n\\nWhen a dropped evaluation is detected (runJobFn line 437), a warning is logged: 'Tick dropped because alert rule evaluation is too slow' (line 438). This indicates the evaluation took longer than its configured interval, causing the scheduler to skip the next scheduled tick. The count of missed evaluations is tracked via metrics.Scheduler.EvaluationMissed (metrics/scheduler.go:178), which increments a counter metric 'schedule_rule_evaluations_missed_total' (line 182) whenever an evaluation cycle overruns its time budget. The scheduler loop itself tracks timing via metrics.BehindSeconds (line 256) to measure scheduler lag, and processTick uses metrics.SchedulePeriodicDuration (line 260) to measure overall tick processing time.\"\n}\n",
